同科水都聽過<br />\n科金真係第一次</blockquote><br />\n正想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣講法？<br />\nBtw 除左樓豬夾唔到之外睇唔出有邊到黑店法"},{"pid":"65d2731ab72e26e4ed31156b2123f2a8a2b171a8","tid":295422,"uid":15481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T20:46:44.000Z","msg":"今日先係大阪返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb912c88a219f5051685903b8aaf186cb44f211a","tid":295422,"uid":17387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T20:52:10.000Z","msg":"係大路d既鋪<br />\n個職員見你夾極都夾唔到<br />\n會整到勁易比你夾<br />\n什至會直程開機拎隻比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdb33b0769d0b7d91c93b241aaa5ceffb842436","tid":295422,"uid":54485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T21:09:36.000Z","msg":"屌你咁撚大間Sega唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b3481d7d7172102361221f8272abf13e5aa1cd","tid":295422,"uid":56511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T21:24:37.000Z","msg":"你情我願何來黑店？"},{"pid":"15093216512bd391b9a5823abea8e668d9fe872c","tid":295422,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T21:30:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你情我願何來黑店？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n格嚟post話一皮港紙都夾唔到就話啫<br />\n呢個一皮yen嘅話我都未見到黑店個位係邊<br />\n<br />\n不如樓豬post埋上網睇到果幾個經歷嚟睇下"},{"pid":"325a6e8f23041029392fa89baa53a99ab05e0f0c","tid":295422,"uid":8497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T21:32:46.000Z","msg":"自尾廢又要屈人<br />\n人地送張卷比你玩多次都要話人黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd356be036aae581bcc86d51e48abd4a785202c","tid":295422,"uid":21204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T21:37:08.000Z","msg":"去電電城啦 有幾間良心企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}